title: Red Raiders primed for NCAA Tournament - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Red Raiders primed for NCAA Tournament - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: WINSTON-SALEM, N.C. -- The Texas Tech men's tennis team is gearing up for the first round of the NCAA tournament against Auburn Friday at 1 p.m. (ET)/Noon (CT) at the Wake Forest Tennis Center.
